title: Top Floor 1 Bedroom Apartment Available September 17th!
posting_body: ['Silver Lake Apartments is proudly managed by Bigos Management!', 'You can reach us at', 'show contact info', 'or check us out online at <URL>.', 'Apartment 28-301 is a spacious 1 Bedroom apartment on the third floor.', 'We are conveniently located near grocery stores, parks, and walking trails with very easy access to highways and interstates.', 'Rent is only $1065 for a 18-month lease.', 'Flexible lease terms available.', '"Please note, pricing is subject to change daily.', 'Adjusting your move-in date or lease term will adjust pricing.', 'Payment of the application fee will lock the rental rate for only the selected lease term and move-in date."', 'Our Office Hours are Monday - Saturday 9:00am-5:00pm', 'Rent Includes:', '~All utilities except electricity', '~Outdoor pool, grills, picnic area, off street parking, and 24 hour laundry rooms!', 'Security Deposit: $400.00', 'Administration Fee: $150.00', 'Application Fee: $50.00 per applicant', 'Application Requirements:', '-Full Criminal Background Check', '-Full Credit Background Check', '-Income Qualification (Gross income must be;', 'Apartment Rent * 2.5)', '-Rental History (Looking for at least 1 positive year )', '-Occupancy Limits (No more than 2 people for every 1 bedroom)', '**PLEASE BRING IN A COPY OF THIS AD WHEN YOU VISIT TO RECEIVE AN', 'ADDITIONAL $150 OFF YOUR FIRST MONTH’S RENT***', 'For more information about this available apartment or our community feel free to give us a call at', 'show contact info', 'or check us out online at <URL>.']
